-lot-of-kids-dont-know-what-concert-etiquette-is-3480567">史蒂夫·莱西打破了相机，并拒绝为他认为的糟糕的音乐会礼仪道歉</a>。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-grips-cut-short-us-concert-after-getting-hit-by-glowsticks-3515333">在粉丝向乐队投掷荧光棒和显然是一部手机</a>后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-grips">Death Grips</a>停止了在阿肯色州的演出。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Netflix 正在与 Take-Two Interactive 洽谈为其订阅服务开发和发布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/netflix-in-talks-for-grand-theft-auto-spin-off-game-3516407"><em>《侠盗猎车手》</em>衍生游戏</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/knocked-loose-fans-bring-runescape-and-nintendo-ds-consoles-to-live-shows-3516436">《Knocked Loose》粉丝将“RuneScape”和 Nintendo DS 游戏机带到现场表演的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
